📗 A poeo structure to define command parameters. 📗
🌍 🕊 📎 🍇
  💭 init
  🖍🆕 name 🔡
  🖍🆕 description 🔡
  🖍🆕 key 🔡
  🖍🆕 short 🍬🔡
  🖍🆕 default 🍬🔡
  🖍🆕 isFlag 👌
  🖍🆕 isRequired 👌

  💭 init
  🆕
    🍼 name 🔡
    🍼 description 🔡
    🍼 key 🔡
    🍼 short 🍬🔡
    🍼 default 🍬🔡
    🍼 isFlag 👌
    🍼 isRequired 👌
  🍇🍉


  💭 getters
  📗 Gets the parameter name 📗
  🔓 ❓ 📛 ➡️  🔡 🍇
    ↩️ name
  🍉
  📗 Gets the parameter description 📗
  🔓 ❓ 💬 ➡️  🔡 🍇
    ↩️ description
  🍉
  📗 Gets the key used in the command line for the parameter 📗
  🔓 ❓ 🔑 ➡️  🔡 🍇
    ↩️ key
  🍉
  📗 Gets the short single letter identifier for the parameter used in the command line 📗
  🔓 ❓ 🧒 ➡️  🍬🔡 🍇
    ↩️ short
  🍉
  📗 Gets the default value for the parameter if no value is passed 📗
  🔓 ❓ 🚗 ➡️  🍬🔡 🍇
    ↩️ default
  🍉
  📗 Gets a bool value if the parameter is a simple boolean flag 📗
  🔓 ❓ 🚩 ➡️  👌 🍇
    ↩️ isFlag
  🍉
  📗 Gets a bool value if the parameter is required 📗
  🔓 ❓ 🧠 ➡️  👌 🍇
    ↩️ isRequired
  🍉
🍉
